{
  "stem": "10572.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "While other friends of ours who were more flexible and more mobile-- physically and emotional-- said, this is too ridiculous.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We pack and leave.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We saw at that time some very interesting things happening.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We saw people who had never known that they were Jewish suddenly became not Jews-- Jews but became fanatic Zionists because they felt that there was-- their-- their lack or their-- their being-- being a secular Jew, it was much easier for them to become a Zionist than to become a religious Jew.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And many of them, in the first months or in the first year of the Hitler came to power, left Germany and went to, at that time, Palestine.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And many of them left while they were still able to take their money out and left and went to South America or went to America.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we stuck it out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think they were-- I think they were much more realistic.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We called it at that time much more pessimistic than we were.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they were much more realistic than we were.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we made them wishful thinking for a long, long time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all of this was a little bit emphasized by the fact that in September 1933-- so that is about nine months after Hitler came to power-- we got one of the coveted awards for one of the fashion creations that we sent to Berlin.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was, at that time, it was almost unbelievable that a Jewish firm would be so rewarded.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was at the same time-- it was not only an uplift for our own spirits, you know, we said, you know, you see, they are not all Nazis.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and-- and the people who gave us this award were not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
